snippet.title: Arcade Game: Kick Rider (1984 Universal)
snippet.description: A motorbike-racing game viewed from the above. You control a motorbike racing against opponents such as occasional cars and motorcycilists who jostle you with their legs. You earn points by racing against the clock for points.
